__6 Cents__ - This stamp is rated as the second most expensive of this Issue in the Catalogue. It is rare either in an unused or used condition, and blocks, in particular are very scare. Figure 4 is an example of the 6-cent stamps used on cover (from Penang to Zoerlohm, Austria). 
This is the second cover I have ever seen with a 6-cent stamp.

