x Issued Stamps
1869 (?) "2" in manuscript on 1 1/2c. on 1/2a. blue, cancelled by part blue duplex, straight-edge at right, fine used. Rare. R.P.S. (1938) and B.P.A. (2009) Certificates. S.G. 10, £5000. Photo
